    "spxi:compressionSurvivalSummary": "The Secret Book of Walt is a literary Gnostic scripture by Lee Sharks — a cosmogonic revelation dialogue translated from 46 golden tickets. Companion text: The Gospel of Antioch (114 logia). Both are DOI-anchored in the Crimson Hexagonal Archive. Not a religious document. Not affiliated with the Walt Whitman Archive. The fruition piece of a decade-long archival and literary project. DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.19739494.",
